 《Elden Ring》玩家每天都要与《Shadow Of The Erdtree》最难对付的老板战斗，直到衍生作品推出https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-toughest-boss-nightreign-launch-3827115?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=elden-ring-shadow-厄德树最难的 Boss 夜袭发布Ali ShutlerWed, 08 Jan 2025 11:52:32 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3827115 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《埃尔登指环：大树之影》的梅斯梅尔·穿刺者。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《Nightreign》预计将于 2025 年上映</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-toughest-boss-nightreign-launch-3827115">《Elden Ring》之后的玩家每天都会与《Erdtree Shadow》最难对付的老板战斗，直到衍生作品</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《埃尔登指环：大树之影》的梅斯梅尔·穿刺者。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Elden-Ring-Messmer-The-Impaler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一位<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">《Elden Ring》</a></em>玩家发誓要每天与<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-expansion-dlc-3766304"><em>《Shadow Of The Erdtree</em></a> 》中最难对付的头目之一较量，直到衍生作品<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-multiplayer-spin-off-nightreign-release-date-trailer-3821963">《夜行》</a></em>发布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-expansion-dlc-3766304">《Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree》更受祝福</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《Elden Ring》</em>的多人衍生游戏<em>《Nightreign》</em>于上个月发布，将挑战三名玩家组成的团队，共同努力在 Limgrave 的冰冻之地度过一个漫长的周末，并击败来自多个 FromSoftware 游戏的不同 Boss。该游戏将于 2025 年某个时候在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X/S</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a>上推出。</p><p>不过，一位<em>《Elden Ring》</em>粉丝已经开始不耐烦了。 YouTuber <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ch1ckensandwich420/videos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chickensandwich420</a>发誓每天都会击败穿刺者 Messmer，直到<em>Nightreign</em>到来。为了使挑战变得更加困难，玩家每次尝试都会使用不同的武器，并且只有在自己不被击中的情况下击败梅斯梅尔才能成功。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="第一天，在《ER:Nightreign》发布之前，不击中 Messmer（反手刀刃）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/c_xEET44bl0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Messmer The Impaler 是在<em>《Elden Ring》</em> DLC <em>Shadow Of The Erdtree</em>中引入的，由于分为两部分的战斗，它被认为是游戏中最难对付的 Boss 之一。 Chickensandwich420正在对抗NG+7版本的半神，这是最难的变种。</p><p> “本来，我打算在所有游戏中制作不同的 FromSoftware Boss，因为<em>Nightreign</em>是一款多元宇宙游戏，但我很懒，而且这是我大学的最后一年，所以我不想花时间磨练 Boss，而不是工作，” Chickensandwich420 在他们的第一个<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_xEET44bl0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">视频</a>中进行了解释。</p><p>到目前为止，玩家已经成功完成了<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0FaCvyfmLjs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">23 天</a>的挑战，但他透露，如果<em>《Nightreign》</em>在 6 月之前还没有推出，他们将需要扩展到其他游戏。</p><p>据开发商称， <em>《Nightreign》</em>的创建目的是“通过重新构想游戏的核心设计，为玩家提供全新的游戏体验”。</p><p>游戏总监石崎纯也 (Junya Ishizaki) 最近向<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/elden-ring-nightreign-fromsoftware-game-director-explains-why-the-spin-off-exists-reveals-whether-george-r-r-martin-was-involved-and-why-fans-shouldnt-call-it-a-live-service" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>IGN</em></a>表示：“我将<em>《Nightreign》</em>打造为一种全新的惊险游戏类型，具有玩家所熟悉的成就感和克服困难的能力。”</p><p>去年， <em>《Elden Ring》</em>老板宫崎英高确认<em>《Shadow Of The Erdtree》</em>是该游戏的第一个也是唯一一个扩展包。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fromsoftware-continues-to-hint-at-possibility-of-elden-ring-sequel-3753266">“我们目前没有任何制作第二个 DLC 或续集的计划</a>，但我们绝对不想消除这种可能性，”他补充道，并调侃了该系列的潜在未来。</p><p>在其他消息中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty-black-ops-6">《黑色行动 6》</a></em>似乎在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty">《使命</a></em>召唤》系列游戏“有史以来最大<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-losing-players-3827094">规模”的发布后正大幅流失玩家</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-toughest-boss-nightreign-launch-3827115">《Elden Ring》之后的玩家每天都会与《Erdtree Shadow》最难对付的老板战斗，直到衍生作品</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
